data.description: Welcome to your dream home in desirable Fredrick Farms. This 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath ranch style home offers a beautiful stone and brick exterior, large great room with cathedral ceilings and gas log fireplace. Kitchen with flush bar top, QUARTZ counter tops, white upgraded cabinets, huge pantry and stainless steel appliances. Large laundry room with laundry sink and folding area next to mud room with lockers and access to 1/2 bath. Master bedroom with tray ceiling, large walk in closet, tile walk in shower, and two vanities. Two additional bedrooms and full Jack and Jill bathroom. 4th bed room/den/office is located in front of home. Enjoy your large back patio over looking privacy fenced yard with wooden playhouse and playset. Rain bird sprinkler system in front yard.  All of this with a 3 car garage!
